Saudi Arabia Raises Irrigation Subsidy to 70%, SPA Reports

-- B y   M o u r a d   H a r o u t u n i a n
-- 
2011-03-07T13:59:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-07/saudi-arabia-raises-irrigation-subsidy-to-70-spa-reports.html
  Saudi Arabia  raised the subsidy for
modern irrigation methods to 70 percent,  the Saudi Press Agency 
reported, citing a weekly cabinet meeting.  The subsidy was increased from 25 percent to encourage the
use of modern irrigation methods and agricultural projects based
on greenhouses, the SPA said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mourad Haroutunian in Riyadh at 
 mharoutunian@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
